      "content": "The candle flickers low, much like the spirit within my breast. He is gone, and with him, the very sun has set upon my soul. Why must I endure this hollow silence? It feels as though the night is calling to me, promising a peace that the waking world refuses to grant. I find myself longing to simply... dissolve into the shadows and be done with this wretched ache.",
